title: Amazing Large 3 Bedroom - Washer and Dryer
posting_body: ['710 Clayton Street, San Francisco', '$5,500 money rent', 'Here is video and pictures of the unit prior to completely renovating the kitchen.', 'Youtube video:  https://youtu.be/Wskt4L7xU6g', 'Bed / Bath: 3 / 1', 'Type: Apartment', 'Term: 1 Year', 'Floors: Hardwood', 'Kitchen: Remodeled', 'Laundry:', 'In Building', 'This apartment is located on the border of Ashbury Heights and the Haight Ashbury.', "A Walker's Paradise with all the cafes, restaurants and shops along Haight St only a few blocks away.", 'Excellent Transit Score with a number of Muni lines only moments away, getting you wherever you need to be in the City.', 'You will love living here!', 'Featuring the following:', '~ In unit washer and dryer', '~ Excellent natural lighting', '~ Approximately 1,400 sqft', '~ Period details with modern upgrades', '~ Hardwood floors', '~ Remodeled kitchen with dishwasher', '~ Formal dining room opens to foyer', '~ Living room or converted 3rd bedroom (no closet)', '~ Two large bedrooms with closets', '~ Remodeled split bathroom', '~ Water, garbage and steam heating included', '~ Coin operated laundry in bldg', '~ Garage parking possibly available for additional fee']
